178
00:12:04,181 --> 00:12:05,307
Hoy!

179
00:12:05,391 --> 00:12:06,559
Huwag madala.

180
00:12:06,642 --> 00:12:07,560
Pakinggan mo ako.

181
00:12:07,643 --> 00:12:10,062
Sa tingin ko, may pinagkakaabalahan tayo. Shamanism!

182
